            "licence-</listIntroduction>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec43-sub3-lst1-itma\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" +
            "<num>(a)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>shall be in the prescribed form;</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</item" +
            ">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec43-sub3-lst1-itmb\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<num>(b)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<" +
            "p>shall be subject to such conditions as may be prescribed or\r\n                 " +
            "                       authorized by the rules regulating the manner, place or\r\n" +
            "                                        hours in, at or during which the license" +
            "d business may be\r\n                                        carried on and the tr" +
            "ophies or class of trophies which may\r\n                                        b" +
            "e dealt in;</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</item>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec43-sub3-lst1-itmc\">\r\n\t\t\t\t" +
            "\t\t\t\t\t<num>(c)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>shall be subject to the payment of the prescrib" +
            "ed fee, and\r\n                                        different fees may be presc" +
            "ribed for different classes of\r\n                                        dealers;" +
            "</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</item>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec43-sub3-lst1-itmd\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<num>(" +
            "d)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>shall, subject to any other provision of this Act, be vali" +
            "d\r\n                                        for a period of twelve months from th" +
            "e date of issue\r\n                                        thereof.</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<" +
            "/item>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</blockList>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</content>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</subsection>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<subsect" +
