            "\t\t\t<content>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>(Subject to <ref id=\"ref46\" href=\"#sec44-sub3\">subsectio" +
            "n (3)</ref>,\r\n                                no person shall transfer the owner" +
            "ship of any trophy to any other\r\n                                person by way o" +
            "f gift, sale or otherwise unless he is in possession\r\n                          " +
            "      of a certificate of ownership in respect of the trophy and unless,\r\n      " +
            "                          at the time of the transfer, he endorses the certifica" +
            "te with the\r\n                                date of transfer and the name of th" +
            "e person to whom the trophy is\r\n                                transferred and " +
