            "ng ten thousand shillings or to\r\n                                imprisonment fo" +
            "r a term not exceeding twelve months or to both.</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</content>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</s" +
            "ubsection>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<subsection id=\"sec44-sub3\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<num>(3)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<cont" +
            "ent>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nothing in this section shall apply to any transfer of ownership" +
            " of a\r\n                                trophy by operation of law or in conseque" +
