            "st id=\"sec45-sub1-lst1\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<listIntroduction>No person shall export any l" +
            "ive protected animal, of game\r\n                                animal or game bi" +
            "rd except-</listIntroduction>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec45-sub1-lst1-itma\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" +
            "\t\t<num>(a)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>through a customs port of entry; and</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t" +
            "</item>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec45-sub1-lst1-itmb\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<num>(b)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t" +
