            "istIntroduction>Nothing in this section shall apply to any animal or trophy whic" +
            "h\r\n                                is-</listIntroduction>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<item id=\"sec" +
            "45-sub4-lst1-itma\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<num>(a)</num>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>in transit through Ken" +
